          "INC-SPECT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".Angles of irradiation of the target by deuterium ion",
                " beam are 0, 30, 60, 90, 120 and 130 degrees. Effective",
                " mean neutron energy at each sample position had been",
                " previously determined by the ratio of 90Zr(n,2n)89Zr",
                " and 93Nb(n,2n)92M-Nb cross sections",
                ".Neutron fluxes ranged from 1.E+7 to 6.E+7 n/cm2/sec"
              ]
            }
          ],
